We believe our team has the ability to utilize our broad portfolio of brands, highly effective sales force and key strategic partnerships to continue providing adult consumers an exciting array of high quality products.  We also believe that our employees are the most essential contributors to our success.  We want to empower people to do good work and to make meaningful contributions to the company.  When you join Turning Point Brands, you are joining a collaborative team of professionals that encourage each other to do their best and have fun while doing it.  We are truly excited that you have decided to pursue a career with our team.













