Age Control Policy
































Turning Point believes that tobacco use or nicotine consumption in any form are adult activities. Accordingly, the Company reiterates its long-standing policy that neither it nor its subsidiaries will engage in tobacco product advertising, marketing or promotion that is directed toward or intended to appeal to persons below age 21. In line with that policy, for any purchased or shipped products, the Company employs extensive age verification processes and will not sell or ship to any consumer under 21 years of age. Moreover, the Company markets its products for particular uses and gives instructions and directions regarding the use of its products, and does not encourage consumption of the products not in conformance with that guidance.
NOTIFICATION OF AGE RESTRICTED SITE. All Turning Point tobacco subsidiaries notify visitors to their respective websites that they are age restricted sites intended for tobacco consumers 21 years of age or older. This notification appears on the first page that visitors see when they come to the site.











